OL,3,CGrieving mother campaigns for vaccine
OL,4,Cprogramme after losing son to
OL,5,Cmeningitis
OL,7,FA grieving mother is calling on the
OL,8,Fgovernment to vaccinate as many young
OL,9,Fpeople as possible, after losing her
OL,10,Fson Alfie to Meningitis.
OL,12,FMarissa Mullans described Alfie, an 18-
OL,13,Fyear-old student studying at Bury
OL,14,FCollege, as 'the most perfect son'.
OL,16,FShe said: "He was just kind, caring
OL,17,Fand thoughtful. And we just miss him
OL,18,Fbeyond words."
