OL,3,CGrieving mother campaigns for vaccine
OL,4,Cprogramme after losing son to
OL,5,Cmeningitis
OL,7,FHe became unwell last June, and within
OL,8,F14 hours he passed away after being
OL,9,Ftaken to A&E.
OL,11,FMarissa is now campaigning to
OL,12,Fvaccinate as many young people as
OL,13,Fpossible who did not receive the
OL,14,FMeningitis B vaccine as a child.
OL,16,FAlfie did not show many of the
OL,17,Fsymptoms often linked to Meningitis,
OL,18,Fbut he returned from college with a
OL,19,Fheadache.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
