OL,7,FMarissa said: "He didn't feel too
OL,8,Fgreat so he was going to go and have a
OL,9,Flie down".
OL,11,F"We noticed a tiny little rash about
OL,12,Fthe size of a 10 pence piece on
OL,13,FAlfie's chest."
OL,15,FMarissa said they began to think then
OL,16,Fthat it could be meningitis, and took
OL,17,FAlfie to A&E where they took him to
OL,18,Fthe resuscitation unit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
