OL,7,F"I remember asking the nurse if he's
OL,8,Fgoing to be ok, and the nurse
OL,9,Fresponded 'we're going to do
OL,10,Feverything we can' and it was at that
OL,11,Fmoment... you don't want to hear that
OL,12,Ffrom a nurse," she said.
OL,14,FThe hospital team tried to get an
OL,15,Farterial line into Alfie's wrist to
OL,16,Fadminister the medication, before
OL,17,Fputting him into an induced coma.
OL,19,FBut, Alfie began to rapidly
OL,20,Fdeteriorate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
