OL,7,FMarissa said: "The consultant came out
OL,8,Fto say that Alfie's heart had stopped.
OL,10,F"I think I was just in shock at that
OL,11,Fpoint, so I did go back into the room
OL,12,Fand I stood there and watched them
OL,13,Fworking on Alfie for about half an
OL,14,Fhour... and then they called time".
OL,16,FSaturday 5 October will be World
OL,17,FMeningitis Day, and Marissa is hoping
OL,18,Fto raise awareness of the condition.
