OL,7,FMarissa said: "He brought nothing but
OL,8,Fkindness and happiness into my life,
OL,9,Fand as part of a legacy for Alfie, I
OL,10,Fwant to make a different and stop
OL,11,Fother people from having to go through
OL,12,Fwhat we're going through."
OL,14,FShe is calling on the government to
OL,15,Frun a health campaign around symptoms
OL,16,Fof Meningitis and the signs to look
OL,17,Fout for.
OL,19,FWhile the vaccine is available on the
OL,20,FNHS, this was only introduced from
OL,21,F2015.
