OL,8,Fto introduce a 'catch-up programme' to
OL,9,Fvaccinate all those born before 2015.
OL,11,FShe said: "Vaccinations are not fool-
OL,12,Fproof, but as a mother who's lost her
OL,13,Fchild, I would want my child to have
OL,14,Fan extra layer of protection."
